ss="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><!-- Link Gitalk 的支持文件  --><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/gitalk/dist/gitalk.css"><script src="https://unpkg.com/gitalk@latest/dist/gitalk.min.js"></script> <div id="gitalk-container"></div>     <script type="text/javascript">    var gitalk = new Gitalk({<pre><code>// gitalk的主要参数    clientID: 1a7728b1104b0f4fe48c,    clientSecret: 8e513bd2539e15ff0f89c837d6ae385af1c8edc4,    repo: https://jiujiu-donotwanttogrowup.github.io/,    owner: jiujiu-DoNotWantToGrowUp,    admin: [jiujiu-DoNotWantToGrowUp],    id:decodeURI(window.location.pathname),&#125;);gitalk.render(&#39;gitalk-container&#39;);</code></pre><p></script> </p><!-- Gitalk end --><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html">Deployment</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
